@startuml
state "Select Withdrawal Amount" as SelectAmount
state "Enter Custom Value" as EnterCustomValue
state "Verify Transaction" as VerifyTransaction
state "Re-enter Amount" as ReenterAmount

SelectAmount --> EnterCustomValue: User chooses custom value
SelectAmount --> VerifyTransaction: User selects an option

VerifyTransaction --> ReenterAmount: Transaction rejected
VerifyTransaction --> [*]: Transaction verified

ReenterAmount --> SelectAmount: User re-enters amount
@enduml
